			Profile
			
			HenglinChen&nbsp;receivedtheB.S.andM.S.degreesinmaterialscienceandengineeringfromTianjinUniversity,Tianjin,China,in2000and2003,respectively,andthePh.D.degreeinelectricalengineeringfromZhejiangUniversity,Hangzhou,China,in2007.FromJanuary2008toSeptember2009,hewasaPostdoctoralResearcherattheCollegeofElectricalEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity.&nbsp;InOctober2009,hejoinedtheFacultyofPowerElectronicsInstituteofZhejiangUniversityasaLecturer.InDecember2011,hewaspromotedtoanAssociateProfessor.
Hismainresearchinterests&nbsp;focuseon&nbsp;electromagneticcompatibility(EMC)inpowerelectronicsystems.
Dr.ChenreceivedtheDeltaVisitingScholarAwardfromtheDeltaEnvironmentalandEducationalFoundationin2010.
			
				
			Researchwork
			
			EMIModelingandMitigationforPowerElectronics;
Near-FieldEMIModelingandSuppressionforPowerConverters;
EMIFilterDesignforAC-DCConverters.
			
				
